title: Something we want to tell you!
author: AmazingPhil
description:
Where has Dan been?! What are our future plans? The TRUTH IS REVEALED! Download Stereo and follow me and listen to the after party at 9PM! http://stereo.com/AmazingPhil (Stereo is an age 18 and over app) thanks to Stereo for this paid promotion!

A big Dan and Phil catchup! Like a mukbang but with no gross eating sounds. 

Pre-Order Dan's book! https://www.danandphilshop.com/collections/newest/products/pre-order-you-will-get-through-this-night-with-free-art-card comes with a FREE art card and bookmark!
